{"article_id":"rGXaG1fnTgbIrfKh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The U.S. reported the highest coronavirus death toll in the world as of Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"per Johns Hopkins data .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"18,860 Americans have died .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The big picture :","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Europeans and Americans are desperate to move beyond the worst of the crisis","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"and return to something","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"approximating normal ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"but the World Health Organization has cautioned","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that moving too fast will undermine sacrifices","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"made so far .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"By the numbers :","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"There have been over 390,000 global recoveries .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The U.S. has reported the most cases","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"( over 503,500 )","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and deaths","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"( over 19,700 ) .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Spain had reported the most cases outside the U.S.","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"( more than 161,000 ) .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Half the planet 's population is on lockdown .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"What 's happening :","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"Crime is dropping around the world","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"as the coronavirus keeps people home","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"-","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"but police around the globe are taking extra efforts","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"to enforce social distancing over Easter weekend .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Food shortages in richer countries and hunger in poorer ones could be caused by the crisis ,","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"as some crops rot in fields","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"and others are subject to export bans .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"in richer countries and hunger in poorer ones could be caused by the crisis ,","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"as some crops rot in fields","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"and others are subject to export bans .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"In India , people are able to see blue skies for the first time in years","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"as the country 's three-week lockdown has drastically cut air pollution .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"people are able to see blue skies for the first time in years","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"as the country 's three-week lockdown has drastically cut air pollution .","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"Iran started reopening government buildings on Saturday","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"after a brief lockdown .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"started reopening government buildings on Saturday","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"after a brief lockdown .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"China 's shipments of N95 respirators , ventilators , hospital gowns and other products face new delays .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"of N95 respirators , ventilators , hospital gowns and other products face new delays .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"South Korea has threatened to track residents with electronic wristbands","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"if they break self-quarantine .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"has threatened to track residents with electronic wristbands","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"if they break self-quarantine .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"A Good Friday ceremony was held at the Notre Dame","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"to provide a `` message of hope . '' was held at the Notre Dame","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"to provide a `` message of hope . ''","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"The U.K. reported its highest daily rise in coronavirus deaths on Friday , with 980 dead within 24 hours .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Prime Minister Boris Johnson is out of intensive care .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"reported its highest daily rise in coronavirus deaths on Friday , with 980 dead within 24 hours .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Prime Minister Boris Johnson is out of intensive care .","dep